{"tid":519466,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"［live] 攝影白痴漫遊九州山陰中部北陸十二日","createTime":"2018-01-04T11:25:01.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-16T06:36:24.000Z","uid":109434,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"e1111b57d0e6ff3b3eedf21c5744809648112cab","tid":519466,"uid":109434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-04T11:25:01.000Z","msg":"今次係第二次自己一個黎日本啦，成日睇大家嘅遊記 ，成日諗如果我寫嘅話我好大可能會半途而廢，所以今次po上黎就係逼自己唔好放棄<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n先聲明下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 因為我成日食屎嘅體質<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我已經做定心理準備會有好多on9野發生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 第二就係我係比所有friend唾棄嘅影相白痴，所有嘅相係我用iphone9影嫁炸，唔好要求太高<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n行程大概係咁：<br />\n4/1 廣島 原爆圓頂+平和紀念館+長田堂廣島燒<br />\n5/1 宮島 嚴島神社+表參道》松江 縣立美術館日落<br />\n6/1 松江 割子蕎麥麵》境港 紅楚蟹任食<br />\n7/1 境港 紅楚蟹特別定食》米子 足立美術館<br />\n8/1 鳥取 浦富海岸+猛者蝦會宴+砂丘+沙之美術館<br />\n9/1 大阪 雞白湯拉麵》京都 伏見稻荷+祗園花見小路<br />\n10/1 京都 金閣寺+嵯峨野電車+嵐山大街 豆腐稻定食<br />\n11/1 京都 銀閣寺+鞍馬貴船散策<br />\n12/1 高山 白川鄉+相倉部落<br />\n13/1 金澤 morimori sushi+近江町市場<br />\n14/1 做task買呢買路<br />\n15/1 bye<br />\n<br />\n今朝到步之後搭機場1號巴係廣島巴士中心落車 ，第一日睇原爆記念館同原爆dome<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n一落機就on9咗，特登帶咗個暖水杯諗住呢個trip飲熱水養下生。本身以為便利店無得斟熱水，咁我就用左100yen買杯茶keep起個茶包要啲熱水啦，跟手一買完就見到成個熱水壼放係收銀檯隔離（後尾我發現間間便利店都會放個壺比人斟水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ）任斟唔洗錢屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n一路由機場出市區，兩邊都係樹林同山坡，個天清到不得了，啲雲好似核桃咁一粒粒好立體。<br />\n<br />\n連埋上幾次搭巴士，我開始發現日本人坐巴士除非係識或者情侶或者夫婦，否則都唔會男女一齊坐連位，otherwise咁樣做大家係會對你行注目禮的<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n落車之後本來打算長田屋廣島燒》原爆dome》紀念館，去到個時2點左右長田屋出面條人龍，再加埋之前係北海道見識過日本人有幾咁鐘意排隊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 之後，我果斷放棄咗食佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n和平紀念公園好受歐美人歡迎 因為平時係日本其他地方好少見咁多歐美遊客 呢度差唔多大部分都係歐美嘅旅客<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/04/191153_8b100b703cd6c16693d16d3371bfec78.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F04%2F191153_8b100b703cd6c16693d16d3371bfec78.jpg&h=24744d52&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n呢個慰靈埤係正對住原爆dome的，行前多幾步會見到有個火盤長期燒住，象徵上香（？）呢個儀式<br />\n<br />\n到紀念館啦，其實紀念館比我想像中無咁震撼，可能因為入面內容比較淺，切合番加深大眾理解個原意。個館多數簡單講atomic bomb嘅原理、投彈嘅政治談判過程同埋歷史野。因為我中學physics叫做學過atomic bomb原理，讀U又major政治，所以呢啲資料對於我黎講唔太意外，如果係呢方面無咩認識去會更加適合。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/04/191645_9c52df27d9604c25dd2e6ff5882cbde7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F04%2F191645_9c52df27d9604c25dd2e6ff5882cbde7.jpg&h=8c146d28&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/04/191647_f0a21f7fbac524dd1bb48af31219f63c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F04%2F191647_f0a21f7fbac524dd1bb48af31219f63c.jpg&h=ec598ecd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n原爆dome：歷史意思大於肉眼嘅震撼<br />\n<br />\n所以我好快就睇完個紀念館，先3點幾，我沿住原爆dome行番去長田屋諗住無咩人就去食番，又好彩去到個時我係排第5個 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> （都等咗半個鐘先有得食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ）<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/04/191758_39d8cf5cb7f5ffcebac733744e462ab0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F04%2F191758_39d8cf5cb7f5ffcebac733744e462ab0.jpg&h=e84fbc4c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/04/191759_9dfafab4b5d63ab9b9bf49c363f4c22f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F04%2F191759_9dfafab4b5d63ab9b9bf49c363f4c22f.jpg&h=a74f380d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我就叫咗長田屋燒，豬肉片、蝦仁同魷魚圈急凍貨就緊嫁啦，入面嘅芽菜淋身得黎又有少少爽脆，椰菜仲係好濕潤，仲有生雞蛋，補足番個麵餅煎乾左嘅問題 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 生蔥嘅辛辣同紫蘇嘅香氣 （我個人鐘意食紫蘇額外加嘅）中和咗沙律醬同燒汁嘅膩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 同埋舊野好好好大份，兩個女仔夠食有餘，叫做對得住1500yen個價<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n食完出黎望望 又排番長龍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 總體黎講，平民用料，靠嘅係唔同材料嘅互相配合，係幾好食嘅，不過絕對唔值為咗食佢排1個鐘（咁多人排真係純粹因為日本人鐘意排隊個人意見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ）<br />\n<br />\n完曬今日啲行程，搭電車去宮島口，返酒店抖抖，第日去睇嚴島神社潮漲<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n。<br />\n<br />\n拿，我都話我成日食屎，岩岩諗住拎個細袋仔出去買聽日早餐，個袋條帶就爛q咗，第一日就爛q咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n第一次寫遊記，有咩寫漏寫少咗多多包涵，鐘意嘅禁個<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 啦客官<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b74c5e208fdbcd84927dd4c7fd9b42d34393d3c5","tid":519466,"uid":109434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-04T11:28:58.000Z","msg":"仲有就係呢 我而家用手機出post啲位可能會有啲唔岩都唔定<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n同埋，勿相認<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db6e4e49289e6fb36d2439664a2c51a7a02b6a70","tid":519466,"uid":38591,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-04T11:30:25.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"350139feb743ceb7f21ad75a2fffe7fde11eefa5","tid":519466,"uid":35780,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-04T11:37:59.000Z","msg":"講攝影點可以唔留名!<br />\n<br />\n支持"},{"pid":"9c2b7ebfc51bf0bc109bdd5546714a387f0988ba","tid":519466,"uid":56206,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-10T12:18:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f709805eff27aa94f7ef563d7b5d564376c1e10","tid":519466,"uid":2331,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-10T12:35:05.000Z","msg":"巴打我呢幾日係米子鳥取<br />\n聽日去埋沙丘就落大阪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n呢邊郊到真係普通話都聽少左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb6b29d506e11abc0e6f493f56bf5d6c09b4b7ff","tid":519466,"uid":86764,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-11T03:07:45.000Z","msg":"又話live嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1eac548f7d5c298ecc5e3f5a525109bbacfd9404","tid":519466,"uid":39576,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-11T03:30:32.000Z","msg":"都去好多地方，參考下"},{"pid":"b46e0fd135fdbb37ae6acada4ba0c95446690850","tid":519466,"uid":56206,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-15T16:45:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bab35ed232fe922e54979c1a5cecfd23839f1728","tid":519466,"uid":140481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-16T06:36:24.000Z","msg":"？"}]}